cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to analyze multi-aspect reviews. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with recommendation systems, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
